nodes.text: Alex Lindsay was an Industrial Light & Magic digital effects artist that worked on Star Wars: Episode I The Phantom Menace. In that movie he also played Rum Sleg. Also, he voiced the adult Wicket Wystri Warrick in Tales from the Endor Woods and Mungo Baobab in the Treasure of the Hidden Planet prologue. Today, Alex is head of operations at 090 Media. Before that he founded Pixel Corps. He is also the co-host on the popular Apple podcast on the TWiT Network, Macbreak Weekly.[source?]
